// SKIP: Spell Breaker (2024 PHB Abjurer level 10 feature) not modeled in spec; pMarkBonusActionSpell unconditionally sets bonusActionSpellCast=true regardless of success/slot-expiry, and canCastNonCantripAction checks only not(bonusActionSpellCast) — the spec has no concept of a failed bonus-action spell that leaves the slot unspent being treated differently from a successful one for the one-slot-per-turn restriction.